# Cloudflare Pages security headers for 4c.houseofmastery.co
# (The 4C Personal Task Assessment.)
#
# Rollout strategy (the durable path for a live conversion funnel):
#   * The directives that CANNOT break the app are ENFORCED immediately below
#     via Content-Security-Policy (object-src, base-uri, form-action,
#     frame-ancestors) plus the transport/isolation headers. Zero risk to
#     conversions.
#   * The full resource allowlist ships as Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only
#     so we validate it against real traffic before enforcing. This app loads
#     no external scripts at all — only Google Fonts — so the allowlist is
#     deliberately tiny.
#   * Violations are reported to /api/csp-report (functions/api/csp-report.js)
#     via report-to + the legacy report-uri fallback. Tail them with
#     `wrangler pages deployment tail` during the validation window.
#
# PROMOTE TO ENFORCING once the /api/csp-report stream is clean over real
# traffic: fold the Report-Only allowlist into Content-Security-Policy (merge
# the two policy strings) and delete the Report-Only header.
#
# Allowlist provenance (every origin is referenced in index.html / ghl.js):
#   fonts.googleapis.com  Google Fonts stylesheet (Plus Jakarta Sans)
#   fonts.gstatic.com     Google Fonts files
#   'self'                /api/ghl (CRM capture) + /api/csp-report
#   data:                 Canvas profile-card export (toDataURL)

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), autoplay=(), camera=(), display-capture=(), encrypted-media=(), fullscreen=(self), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
  Reporting-Endpoints: csp-endpoint="/api/csp-report"
  Content-Security-Policy: object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'self' https://*.houseofmastery.co
  Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'self' https://*.houseofmastery.co; upgrade-insecure-requests; report-to csp-endpoint; report-uri /api/csp-report

/manifest.webmanifest
  Content-Type: application/manifest+json; charset=utf-8
